==Tibetan==

===Noun===
'''zobo''' ''or'' '''[[zo bo]]'''  (''plural:'' '''[[zo]]''')
# dzopho (written mdzopho); male of the mdzo a mongrel breed of the yak bull and the common cow.  A kind of domestic cattle reared in Asia for its flesh and milk.  It is a hybrid between the zebu and the yak.

